&lt;p data-start=&quot;132&quot; data-end=&quot;246&quot;&gt;🚪&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;135&quot; data-end=&quot;177&quot;&gt;Garage Door Technician – Charlotte, NC&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;177&quot; data-end=&quot;180&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;180&quot; data-end=&quot;204&quot;&gt;Tip Top Garage Doors&lt;/strong&gt; | &lt;strong data-start=&quot;207&quot; data-end=&quot;221&quot;&gt;Pay Range:&lt;/strong&gt; $20–$24/hour + Bonuses&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;248&quot; data-end=&quot;294&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;248&quot; data-end=&quot;292&quot;&gt;Your next great opportunity starts here!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;296&quot; data-end=&quot;545&quot;&gt;Do you enjoy working with your hands, solving real-world problems, and being the friendly face your neighbors rely on? At &lt;strong data-start=&quot;418&quot; data-end=&quot;442&quot;&gt;Tip Top Garage Doors&lt;/strong&gt;, we’re opening more than just garage doors—we’re opening the door to a fulfilling, rewarding career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;547&quot; data-end=&quot;859&quot;&gt;We’re on the lookout for a positive, personable &lt;strong data-start=&quot;595&quot; data-end=&quot;621&quot;&gt;Garage Door Technician&lt;/strong&gt; ready to grow in a fast-paced, team-first environment. Whether you&#39;re an experienced pro or mechanically inclined and eager to learn, this is your chance to build a future with a company that values integrity, hard work, and community.&lt;/p&gt;
